footer: entries 1-4 (start/end/values/encoding, MS:1003901, sorting_rank 0) UNCHANGED, KEEP the Phase-2
chunk.intensity entry (buffer_format chunk_secondary, MS:1003902, sorting_rank null) verbatim, INSERT a
