   211	## Item 5 — Size sanity
   212	
   213	### Decisions
   214	
   215	- Numpress is materially smaller, matching the ~63% headline. `[VERIFIED]`
   216	
   217	| archive | `spectra_data.parquet` (bytes) | total archive (bytes) |
   218	|---------|-------------------------------:|----------------------:|
   219	| `small.numpress.mzpeak` | 483,960 | 844,899 |
   220	| `small.chunked.mzpeak` (delta) | 1,565,834 | 2,317,492 |
